<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.6">
<l>āḻiyuñcaṅ kumuṭaiyanaṅ kaḷaṭikaḷtām</l>
<l>pāḻimaiyā ṉakaṉavilnam maippakar<supplied>vit</supplied>tār</l>
<l>tōḻiyumnā ṉumoḻiyavai yantuyiṉṟatu</l>
<l>kōḻiyuṅkū kiṉṟatillaikkū riruḷāyiṟṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our god who bears the conch and discus</l>
<l>Spoke to us in a desolate dream.</l>
<l>Except for my confidante and I, the world slept.</l>
<l>The cock had not even crowed; the darkness had become deep.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
